{"questionId":"5275632","questionHtml":"<p>The variation with time of the displacement of an object is shown.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/f7c6432e810b40186769db7d70862d149e931d82.png\"></p>\n<p>What are the average speed and average velocity of the object over the 10 s time interval?</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<table style=\"width:471.65px;height:173px;border-color:#000000;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"2\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:47px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n<td style=\"width:191px;text-align:center;\"><strong>Average speed / m s<sup>−1</sup></strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:210.65px;text-align:center;\"><strong>Average velocity / m s<sup>−1</sup><br></strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:47px;\">A.</td>\n<td style=\"width:191px;text-align:center;\">0.8</td>\n<td style=\"width:210.65px;text-align:center;\">0.8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:47px;\">B.</td>\n<td style=\"width:191px;text-align:center;\">0.8</td>\n<td style=\"width:210.65px;text-align:center;\">1.2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:47px;\">C.</td>\n<td style=\"width:191px;text-align:center;\">1.2</td>\n<td style=\"width:210.65px;text-align:center;\">0.8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:47px;\">D.</td>\n<td style=\"width:191px;text-align:center;\">1.2</td>\n<td style=\"width:210.65px;text-align:center;\">1.2</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>C</p>","meta":{"questionId":"5275632","referenceCode":"23M.1.HL.TZ2.2","subjectId":"46-dp-physics-last-assessment-2024","title":"The variation with time of the displacement of an object is shown. What are the average speed and average velocity of the object over the 10 s time interval? Average speed / m s−1 ","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"2","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["Core","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics","2.1 – Motion","Core","Topic 2: Mechanics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}